为了对SCNA数据进行注释，我们还需要 Protein Coding Gene(PCG)的染色体信息，我是从{bioMart}上下载获取的，当然从别的途径得到也是没有问题的。注释数据基本长介个样子:

  1. 首先我们需要把坑爹的样本 ID 处理了:
library(dplyr)
setwd("PATH")
SCNA <- read.table("LUAD/SCNA.txt", header = T, sep = "\t", stringsAsFactors = F)

SCNA[,1] <- apply(
  as.matrix(SCNA[,1], ncol = 1),
  1,
  function(sample){
    return(paste(strsplit(sample, "-")[[1]][1:3], collapse = "-"))
  }
)
  1. 读入注释文件，利用染色体号，转录本起始和终止位置确定 gene 位置，这里我为了保持健康的内存状况，把结果追加输出:
output_path <- "LUAD/annoed_SCNA.txt"

scna_anno <- function(scna_info){
  chr_name = scna_info[2]
  start = as.numeric(scna_info[3])
  end = as.numeric(scna_info[4])
  match_gene_info = filter(
    PCG_position,
    chromosome_name == chr_name &
    start_position > start &
    end_position < end
  )
  match_gene = unlist(match_gene_info[,1])
  if(length(match_gene) >= 1){
    for(gene in match_gene){
      result = matrix(
        c(scna_info[1], gene, scna_info[6]),
        nrow = 1
      )
      write.table(result, output_path, col.names = F, row.names = F, sep = "\t", quote = F, append = T)
    }
  }
}
apply(
  as.matrix(SCNA, ncol = 6),
  1,
  scna_anno
)
  1. 还是国际惯例，用{igraph}把数据整合成矩阵形式
library(igraph)
annoed_SCNA <- read.table(output_path, header = F, sep = "\t")
SCNA_net <- graph_from_edgelist(as.matrix(annoed_SCNA[, 1:2], ncol = 2), directed = F)
E(SCNA_net)$weight <- unlist(annoed_SCNA[,3])
SCNA_adj <- as_adj(SCNA_net, attr = "weight")
gene_index <- grep("ENSG", rownames(SCNA_adj))
sample_index <- grep("TCGA", colnames(SCNA_adj))
final_SCNA <- SCNA_adj[gene_index, sample_index]
